data.description:
This cozy abode features 3 well-appointed bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, creating a comfortable living space for families or guests. The heart of the home is the inviting living room, complete with a wood-burning fireplace that promises warm, crackling fires on chilly evenings. The kitchen, a blend of functionality and style, boasts elegant granite countertops that complement the modern appliances and white cabinetry. Natural light floods the interiors, enhancing the airy and open feel of the home.

Step outside to discover a backyard designed for relaxation and entertainment. The newly installed fire pit is set on a hardscape circular patio, offering an idyllic spot for gathering under the stars and creating lasting memories. This property blends the warmth of traditional comforts with modern touches, providing a perfect canvas for making it your own. Welcome to a home where every detail adds to the allure of a peaceful and fulfilling lifestyle.
